<br>
I will support the list, regardless of how long it gets because when I was slogging through two weeks of waiting with Patche (my predecessor) then my turn, my right was respected.  Regardless of how much diplomacy and bullshit I had to deal with I got my epic piece and I can say that it was the best two weeks investment of game time I ever made.<br>
<br>
Because of the list I was able to plan vacation time.<br>
<br>
Because of the list I was able to arrange for my guild and helpers to be there and know within 24 hours when it was going to spawn next (having been there for patche's spawn)<br>
<br>
Because of the list I was able to encourage other players to follow the same method to secure their epic pieces with little or no fuss.<br>
<br>
Because of the list I have my epic.<br>
<br>
The list *works*.  It encourages guilds and players to work together rather than against one another.  There has not been one major fight over ragefire since the inception of the list.  There haven't been any hard feelings that I am aware of.  <br>
<br>
*any* cleric that needs my help with ragefire just needs to send me a tell.  I will drop everything to help you as many people did to help me.  (except mlain, he's a moron, what'd you expect, this is a flame board after all)<br>
<br>
Patche, Famodil, Sassami, Gruffnoy...  That was the order when I was camping.<br>
<br>
I hardly ever see you guys around but I'll never forget you because we did it *together*.<br>
<br>
I'm the Famodil guy.<br>
